Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is scheduled for 17 June 2024 at 18:00 CET in the Frankfurt Arena with a capacity of 47,000.
Stadium gates open three hours before kick-off, and mobile tickets are preferred for entry.
No stadium parking is available, and fans are encouraged to use public transport or purchase pre-sale parking tickets.
The stadium is smoke-free and prohibits certain items like large bags, professional cameras, and cane umbrellas.
Cashless transactions are encouraged, and fans should bring valid ID for entry and ticket verification.
